            h2#variations Variations
            p You can place this sidebar in left or right side of your page. By default it's left-sided, but you can simply add <code>sidebar-right</code> class to the <code>.sidebar-boxed</code> tag.
            p Also, by adding <code>sidebar-dark</code> class to the <code>.sidebar-boxed</code> you can change the color of the sidebar.</p>

            h3 Try it

            .btn-group(data-toggle="buttons")
              label#sb-left-side.btn.btn-primary.active
                input(type="radio" name="options" autocomplete="off" checked)
                | Left sided (default)
